        "heading": "Modern Slavery Statement",
        "description": "Human Trafficking, or Modern Slavery as it is often referred to, is a serious crime and a violation of a person\u2019s fundamental human rights. It can take on many forms, including slavery, servitude, forced and compulsory labour or human trafficking, all of which have the common element of depriving a person of their liberty in order to exploit them for personal or commercial gain.",
